data.title: 811 Race St, Cincinnati, Ohio
data.meta_description:
9 reviews of CITYBEAT "this paper tends to have a more liberal bent, however, in the conservatively-charged atmosphere that cincinnati is known for, it makes for a refreshing change, and the writing is very thoughtful and well-informed.  all around, it's a great paper to read for the "other side" of the political spectrum.  

also, great music reviews (including our awesome local music scene), movie and restaurant info...if you're looking for something going on, it gives you the day-to-day layout of what bands are playing where on any given day of the week.  an excellent resource into what's going on around the city."
